I had to return home.

288
00:25:21,561 --> 00:25:23,355
Night can't even stop him.

289
00:25:23,772 --> 00:25:25,357
He likely won't listen to me too.

290
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:27,234
He hates me again.

291
00:25:29,194 --> 00:25:30,278
Gear.

292
00:25:31,404 --> 00:25:33,406
He and I have been through so much.

293
00:25:34,032 --> 00:25:37,536
It was a long and rough path.

294
00:25:39,204 --> 00:25:40,539
I understand.

295
00:25:41,373 --> 00:25:43,833
I just want to have a simple life with him,

296
00:25:44,292 --> 00:25:46,253
but he lost all his memories.

297
00:25:46,294 --> 00:25:48,630
He forgot everything we went through

298
00:25:48,713 --> 00:25:50,882
after that video's incident.

299
00:25:53,176 --> 00:25:54,469
Itt.

300
00:25:54,511 --> 00:25:56,096
Calm down.

301
00:25:56,763 --> 00:25:59,182
As soon as he remembers,

302
00:25:59,224 --> 00:26:00,642
it will end.

303
00:26:02,310 --> 00:26:04,104
He said he doesn't want to remember anymore.

304
00:26:05,230 --> 00:26:06,940
He has to.

305
00:26:07,482 --> 00:26:09,776
I'm not losing Night.

306
00:26:12,279 --> 00:26:13,822
Do you want to lose Day?

307
00:26:14,239 --> 00:26:15,490
No.

308
00:26:18,201 --> 00:26:19,744
But I...

309
00:26:21,705 --> 00:26:23,123
Hey, Itt.

310
00:26:23,832 --> 00:26:25,667
Take a break if you're tired.

311
00:26:26,084 --> 00:26:28,920
You don't need to be strong all the time.

312
00:26:30,714 --> 00:26:32,424
I care about you.

313
00:26:33,174 --> 00:26:34,301
Okay.

314
00:26:35,051 --> 00:26:36,720
Take care.

315
00:27:11,171 --> 00:27:14,090
This is the punishment for your defeat.

316
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,891
Nan!

317
00:27:23,266 --> 00:27:24,392
Whoa!

318
00:27:26,227 --> 00:27:27,437
What's up? Itt.

319
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:29,522
Are you going to faint at my track again?

320
00:27:30,273 --> 00:27:31,274
Hey!

321
00:27:33,318 --> 00:27:35,487
Go get me food.

322
00:27:35,570 --> 00:27:37,322
You can starve to death.

323
00:27:38,239 --> 00:27:39,449
Move!

324
00:27:43,328 --> 00:27:44,454
And...

325
00:27:45,330 --> 00:27:46,706
where's Day?

326
00:27:47,540 --> 00:27:48,917
I came alone.

327
00:27:51,086 --> 00:27:52,796
Are you two good?

328
00:27:54,673 --> 00:27:56,841
Do you still have that video of Mac?

329
00:27:58,968 --> 00:28:00,345
Why?

330
00:28:03,556 --> 00:28:06,267
If you don't want it to come back and haunt you two,

331
00:28:06,559 --> 00:28:08,269
get rid of it.

332
00:28:10,605 --> 00:28:12,065
What happened?

333
00:28:15,944 --> 00:28:17,362
Tell me.

334
00:28:18,196 --> 00:28:19,406
Nothing.

335
00:28:20,448 --> 00:28:22,951
I just don't want you two to have any trouble.

336
00:28:29,624 --> 00:28:31,376
We're fighting.

337
00:28:34,087 --> 00:28:35,922
We're separated now.

338
00:28:38,216 --> 00:28:40,051
He said he wanted to be alone.

339
00:28:41,261 --> 00:28:43,430
Day? Want to be alone?

340
00:28:45,056 --> 00:28:48,727
- Hey! Nan.
- Just go home.

341
00:28:50,061 --> 00:28:52,313
Nan, trust me.

342
00:28:52,397 --> 00:28:53,732
Delete that video.

343
00:28:54,899 --> 00:28:56,359
How can I?

344
00:28:57,193 --> 00:28:59,529
It doesn't even exist.

345
00:29:00,405 --> 00:29:01,531
Huh?

346
00:29:01,573 --> 00:29:03,908
Yeah, I fooled him.

347
00:29:04,701 --> 00:29:05,702
Hm.

348
00:29:05,785 --> 00:29:09,122
Do you feel better now?
Let's go home.

349
00:29:10,206 --> 00:29:13,042
Does Mac know this?

350
00:29:13,752 --> 00:29:14,961
Come on.

351
00:29:15,211 --> 00:29:16,755
I'll find time to tell him.

352
00:29:16,796 --> 00:29:19,257
- When?
- Itt?

353
00:29:19,299 --> 00:29:21,301
- I will.
- When?

354
00:29:21,384 --> 00:29:23,803
You leave for now.
I'll tell him soon.

355
00:29:24,137 --> 00:29:26,264
Just head home.
Go.

356
00:29:26,347 --> 00:29:28,641
- When are you going to tell him?
- I will soon.

357
00:29:28,683 --> 00:29:30,477
- Don't forget that.
- Yeah.

358
00:29:30,810 --> 00:29:32,312
If you don't tell him...

359
00:30:10,058 --> 00:30:11,893
You're late.

360
00:30:12,894 --> 00:30:14,479
Why are you here?

361
00:30:16,105 --> 00:30:18,149
I wanted to talk to you at the racetrack,

362
00:30:18,483 --> 00:30:20,902
but there were some annoying people in the way.

363
00:30:21,361 --> 00:30:23,446
So, I drove to meet you here,

364
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:27,283
but I didn't plan that you'd drive that slowly.

365
00:30:31,704 --> 00:30:33,373
Are you insane?

366
00:30:34,999 --> 00:30:36,084
Cut to the chase.

367
00:30:36,543 --> 00:30:38,169
What do you want?

368
00:30:38,211 --> 00:30:41,256
Tomorrow, I will settle everything with Day.

369
00:30:48,137 --> 00:30:50,056
Don't be fooled twice.

370
00:30:51,015 --> 00:30:54,769
If someone says I'm in danger, do not believe them.

371
00:30:55,061 --> 00:30:59,274
If something bad happens, escape to the safest location.

372
00:30:59,399 --> 00:31:01,192
Do not solo anything.

373
00:31:02,110 --> 00:31:04,362
All these just to lecture me?

374
00:31:04,404 --> 00:31:05,780
Am I supposed to be delighted?

375
00:31:05,864 --> 00:31:06,865
Itt.

376
00:31:08,366 --> 00:31:10,368
If you really are in danger,

377
00:31:10,451 --> 00:31:12,203
I can't leave you.

378
00:31:12,287 --> 00:31:14,330
Care about yourself before caring about me.

379
00:31:14,372 --> 00:31:16,332
This is our mutual agreement.

380
00:31:16,499 --> 00:31:18,751
Day, I won't accept this.

381
00:31:18,793 --> 00:31:21,379
Do not wait for me. Do not waste any time.

382
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:25,383
You need to escape to where there are lots of people.

383
00:31:25,425 --> 00:31:27,719
If you see his car, drive faster.

384
00:31:36,477 --> 00:31:38,354
Don't try that.

385
00:31:38,688 --> 00:31:40,023
That won't work.

386
00:31:40,523 --> 00:31:42,775
I'm not that stupid to use the same trick.

387
00:31:43,484 --> 00:31:46,654
If I want to kidnap you, I could do that right now.

388
00:31:47,739 --> 00:31:48,948
So?

389
00:31:49,449 --> 00:31:52,076
I just informed you so maybe you'd come.

390
00:31:52,577 --> 00:31:55,538
Going or not, what does that have to do with you?

391
00:31:56,664 --> 00:32:00,543
I just want you to see him under my feet.

392
00:32:00,627 --> 00:32:02,253
See him pray for life.

393
00:32:03,212 --> 00:32:05,131
See him all defeated.

394
00:32:12,430 --> 00:32:13,973
Are you a kid?

395
00:32:15,433 --> 00:32:17,101
Seriously.

396
00:32:17,894 --> 00:32:19,854
Are you happy?

397
00:32:20,980 --> 00:32:24,108
Does this resentment make you happy?

398
00:32:25,276 --> 00:32:28,154
All you think about is winning or losing.

399
00:32:28,780 --> 00:32:30,782
Are you happy?

400
00:32:31,616 --> 00:32:34,285
You love to lecture just like Day does.

401
00:32:34,494 --> 00:32:36,245
(That's my business.)

402
00:32:36,829 --> 00:32:39,248
You don't have to come.

403
00:32:41,167 --> 00:32:43,336
I'll record a video for you.

404
00:32:50,593 --> 00:32:51,928
Screw you!

405
00:33:32,969 --> 00:33:34,262
What is wrong with you?

406
00:33:34,345 --> 00:33:36,556
Do you want to die that badly?

407
00:33:45,606 --> 00:33:47,692
Darn it!

408
00:34:19,307 --> 00:34:20,683
Boss, boss.

409
00:34:25,188 --> 00:34:26,355
Boss, boss!

410
00:34:26,981 --> 00:34:28,316
What?

411
00:34:28,524 --> 00:34:29,984
Are you with us?

412
00:34:32,153 --> 00:34:34,489
(Laughing)

413
00:34:34,572 --> 00:34:37,742
With a face like that, you're not with us.

414
00:34:37,825 --> 00:34:40,703
- How about a drink?
- A drink!

415
00:34:40,787 --> 00:34:43,206
What? Are you looking for free drinks?

416
00:34:44,832 --> 00:34:47,502
What kind of person do you think I am?

417
00:34:47,794 --> 00:34:49,545
Freeloader.

418
00:34:50,546 --> 00:34:53,341
You can just disrespect me outright if that's what you think.

419
00:34:53,382 --> 00:34:56,385
- You said it yourself, freeloader!
- Oh!

420
00:34:56,469 --> 00:34:58,596
So harsh.

421
00:34:59,055 --> 00:35:01,641
Sure, I'd like to drink.

422
00:35:01,724 --> 00:35:04,102
- Yeah!
- Yes!

423
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:06,062
Let's go!

424
00:35:07,021 --> 00:35:09,107
What do you mean?

425
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:10,942
The bars haven't opened yet!

426
00:35:11,567 --> 00:35:12,819
Bast!

427
00:35:13,319 --> 00:35:14,695
Let's get to work first. Go!

428
00:35:14,737 --> 00:35:16,781
Both of you. Follow me.

429
00:35:37,468 --> 00:35:38,553
Honey.

430
00:35:39,637 --> 00:35:42,473
Don't let Itt go anywhere today.

431
00:35:44,725 --> 00:35:46,519
Is everything alright?

432
00:35:48,020 --> 00:35:50,857
I'll tell you later.

433
00:35:51,482 --> 00:35:54,318
No matter what. Keep him at home.

434
00:35:55,153 --> 00:35:57,613
I'll be running some errands.

435
00:35:58,072 --> 00:35:59,740
I'll be back late.

436
00:36:05,830 --> 00:36:08,583
Bast, check everything here.

437
00:36:11,127 --> 00:36:13,087
Those down there too.

438
00:36:13,171 --> 00:36:15,214
- Yes.
- Did you see that?

439
00:36:15,798 --> 00:36:19,093
- The old man left!
- What?

440
00:36:19,802 --> 00:36:21,012
Where is Dad going?

441
00:36:21,095 --> 00:36:24,015
Why do you care?

442
00:36:24,098 --> 00:36:28,060
- Let's get some drinks!
- Let's get a drink, Boss!

443
00:36:28,144 --> 00:36:29,687
What did you say?

444
00:36:30,771 --> 00:36:32,106
(Chuckling)

445
00:36:32,773 --> 00:36:35,067
We saw that your son is a bit stressed out

446
00:36:35,151 --> 00:36:39,071
so we're taking him out to decompress.

447
00:36:39,155 --> 00:36:41,073
Right.

448
00:36:41,157 --> 00:36:43,951
I allow you to leave early today.

449
00:36:43,993 --> 00:36:47,580
- Yeah!
- Awesome!

450
00:36:47,997 --> 00:36:50,499
- But Itt, you're not going anywhere.
- What?

451
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,376
Why?

452
00:36:53,419 --> 00:36:55,963
Dad asked that you don't leave home today.

453
00:37:03,763 --> 00:37:07,558
- Cheers!
- Yeah.

454
00:37:08,226 --> 00:37:10,478
Drink some!

455
00:37:11,229 --> 00:37:14,649
Boss, can we have a fun song?

456
00:37:14,732 --> 00:37:15,816
Just one.

457
00:37:16,609 --> 00:37:18,152
He plays. You dance.

458
00:37:23,658 --> 00:37:26,035
Cheers!

459
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:30,039
I'm having so much fun!

460
00:37:31,999 --> 00:37:33,292
Let's have a toast!

461
00:37:33,334 --> 00:37:36,337
- Cheers!
- This is awesome.

462
00:37:36,587 --> 00:37:38,130
- Woo!
- Hey!

463
00:37:38,506 --> 00:37:40,049
Be quiet!

464
00:37:49,684 --> 00:37:52,311
I'm meeting Day at 8 PM tonight.

465
00:37:53,104 --> 00:37:54,522
And?

466
00:37:57,817 --> 00:38:01,279
Your tone tells me you don't believe me.

467
00:38:02,363 --> 00:38:04,407
Once he arrived,

468
00:38:04,949 --> 00:38:07,118
I'll call you so you can hear.

469
00:38:07,451 --> 00:38:08,703
Wait,

470
00:38:09,704 --> 00:38:11,831
or should I video call you?

471
00:38:11,872 --> 00:38:13,833
(Laughing)

472
00:38:13,874 --> 00:38:16,836
It'll be late by the time he arrives.

473
00:38:16,919 --> 00:38:20,840
I am more than free today!

474
00:38:22,633 --> 00:38:25,011
I'll send you the location

475
00:38:25,052 --> 00:38:27,513
just in case you want to see it for yourself.

476
00:38:27,972 --> 00:38:30,182
You're not fooling me, P.

477
00:39:03,424 --> 00:39:06,635
I'm so drunk!

478
00:39:08,846 --> 00:39:10,931
I am not drunk!

479
00:39:23,778 --> 00:39:25,112
Thep!

480
00:39:25,571 --> 00:39:27,156
Thep?

481
00:39:27,239 --> 00:39:28,449
The...

482
00:39:28,532 --> 00:39:31,619
Who are you, lady?
Why are you here?

483
00:39:31,702 --> 00:39:33,537
Thep!

484
00:39:34,246 --> 00:39:36,082
Where is Itt?

485
00:39:37,541 --> 00:39:38,959
K'Itt?

486
00:39:39,001 --> 00:39:42,296
He is gone!
(Laughing)

487
00:39:43,923 --> 00:39:45,716
Gone? To where?

488
00:39:45,716 --> 00:39:48,302
No idea.
(Laughing)

489
00:39:48,844 --> 00:39:50,179
What?

490
00:39:50,221 --> 00:39:53,015
Thank you so much!

491
00:40:13,786 --> 00:40:14,995
Take this.

492
00:40:15,037 --> 00:40:16,247
Boss,

493
00:40:16,330 --> 00:40:17,957
do you want me to hit him?

494
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:20,709
Stay out. Stay here.
Be the lookout.

495
00:40:24,547 --> 00:40:27,550
Boss, I just sent you the video.

496
00:40:29,093 --> 00:40:31,053
Day! What did you do to my dad?

497
00:40:36,517 --> 00:40:38,310
Darn you, P!

498
00:40:42,064 --> 00:40:43,315
You'll be alright.

499
00:40:43,357 --> 00:40:44,650
You'll be safe.

500
00:40:44,733 --> 00:40:45,860
Stay with us.

501
00:40:45,943 --> 00:40:46,902
Itt.

502
00:40:46,944 --> 00:40:49,155
Don't worry. He is safe.

503
00:40:49,238 --> 00:40:50,698
P'Day!

504
00:40:50,781 --> 00:40:53,200
Night, who is that?
